In the technology section I will share my tips and tricks about building a website, mostly in Symfony and Laravel frameworks. If you are a developer, I'm sure you had a time when you faced a problem that took you a while to solve. I spend hours and hours every week just googling and browsing stackoverflow. I will try to post things I find interesting orÂ useful.

